<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Gulf Resources -AMP- Chemical Corp.</ENAMEX> said it agreed to pay <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">$ 1.5 million</ENAMEX> as part of an accord with <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the Environmental Protection Agency</ENAMEX> regarding an environmental cleanup of a defunct smelter the company formerly operated in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Idaho</ENAMEX> .
