The <ENAMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">21 - square - mile</ENAMEX> area is contaminated with lead , zinc and other metals .
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Gulf Resources</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">earlier this year</ENAMEX> proposed a reorganization plan that would make it a unit of a <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Bermuda</ENAMEX> concern , potentially exempting it from liability for the smelter 's cleanup costs .
The company said that as part of its agreement with the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">EPA</ENAMEX> , it `` made certain voluntary undertakings with respect to intercorporate transactions entered into after the reorganization . ''
The company , which issued a statement on the agreement <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">late Friday</ENAMEX> , said that <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">$ 1 million</ENAMEX> of the payment was previously provided for in its financial statements and that $ <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">500,000</ENAMEX> will be recognized in its <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1989 third - quarter</ENAMEX> statement .
