<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Gulf Resources</ENAMEX> added that it `` will seek to recover equitable contribution from others for both the amount of the settlement and any other liabilities it may incur under the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Superfund</ENAMEX> law . ''
Under the agreement , <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Gulf</ENAMEX> must give the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX> government <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">45 days '</ENAMEX> advance written notice before issuing any dividends on common stock .
